{"tid":1650123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（今日紀錄+翻查報導）成日出現嘅直升機：有紅外線熱能探測鏡頭、電子地圖、自動識別系統及機內有綜合系統屏幕","createTime":"2019-10-12T21:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T08:04:32.000Z","uid":50275,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"92d987f11d2ef1f140d16c68c533fd8bcc0535ff","tid":1650123,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:54:14.000Z","msg":"2019.10.12.H175獵豹直升機<br />\n-紅外線熱能探測鏡頭<br />\n-電子地圖<br />\n-自動識別系統<br />\n-機內有綜合系統屏幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ttb3Nj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ttb3Nj.jpg&h=87ac6567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ROOT.hkmedia/videos/1198202917053053/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FROOT.hkmedia%2Fvideos%2F1198202917053053%2F%3Fmodal%3Dadmin_todo_tour&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=5788c9bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ROOT.hkmedia/videos/1198202917053053/?modal=admin_todo_tour</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n機身編號：B-LVJ 。<br />\n<br />\n翻查網上資料，該型號為H175獵豹直升機，屬於政府飛行服務隊，現存7架，法國製造。香港警務處經常召喚飛行服務隊的直升機以進行訓練及行動。"},{"pid":"3d76b5fcd0377a544033a0b7466ea170c3dd99d8","tid":1650123,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:54:24.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n相關報導<br />\n<br />\n明報：<br />\n直升機設有多種特別裝置，包括電子地圖及自動識別系統，電子地圖可快速鎖定目標船隻並提供其速度等資料。直升機機頭下方設有紅外線鏡頭，具拍攝功能，影像會較昔日高清。<br />\n<br />\nHK01：機頭前下方設有具紅外線熱能探測功能的攝影鏡頭。機內有綜合系統屏幕顯示機頭的紅外線攝錄畫面、顯示附近船隻位置及資料的電子地圖、安裝在絞車下方的高清鏡頭畫面等。該電子地圖系統只要瞄準目標船隻，就可以一鍵獲取目標船隻資料。"},{"pid":"d5787a164105be571a82050dd18040eb23b12516","tid":1650123,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited